reviewText:
Michael waddell is number 1 in my book. i'd like to hunt with him, T-bone,
and nick some day. i bought #3 and #4 @ the same time and they are top of the
line. great job guys.....
I liked that the movie arrived fast. It was a gift for my father. I had no dislikes and I recommend that if you like hunting this is the product for you.
